OL,3,CSharp increase in anti-Muslim hatred
OL,4,Cin UK, particularly against women
OL,6,FThe number of Islamophobic incidents
OL,7,Freported to a project monitoring anti-
OL,8,FMuslim abuse in the UK has tripled
OL,9,Fsince the Hamas attacks in Israel last
OL,10,Fyear, the organisation said.
OL,12,FIn almost two-thirds of cases
OL,13,Frecorded, women were the target of
OL,14,Fattacks, showing they "have borne the
OL,15,Fmajority of the brunt" of the abuse,
OL,16,Faccording to Tell Mama, which
OL,17,Fdescribes itself as an independent and
OL,18,Fconfidential support service for
OL,19,Fpeople who face anti-Muslim hatred and
OL,20,Fprejudice across the UK.
