OL,3,CSharp increase in anti-Muslim hatred
OL,4,Cin UK, particularly against women
OL,6,FIt was made aware of 2,010 cases
OL,7,Fbetween October 7 and February 7.
OL,9,FThis was a steep increase compared to
OL,10,Fthe 600 cases reported in the same
OL,11,Ffour-month period the previous year.
OL,13,FOf the total cases recorded after
OL,14,FOctober 7, 1,109 were classed as
OL,15,Fonline cases while 901 took place
OL,16,Foffline, Tell Mama said.
