OL,3,CSharp increase in anti-Muslim hatred
OL,4,Cin UK, particularly against women
OL,6,F"Hate crimes against British Muslims
OL,7,Fhave substantially risen and our data
OL,8,Fclearly demonstrates this," she said.
OL,10,F"This rise in anti-Muslim hate is
OL,11,Funacceptable and we hope that
OL,12,Fpolitical leaders speak out to send a
OL,13,Fclear message that anti-Muslim hate,
OL,14,Flike antisemitism, is unacceptable in
OL,15,Four country."
OL,17,FTell Mama was founded in 2012 and is
OL,18,Fsupported by the Department for
OL,19,FLeveling Up, Housing and Communities.
